{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"title":"Pancakes","content":["Place flour, cocoa powder, sugar and salt in mixing bowl then mix <nobr>10 sec\/speed 7<\/nobr>.","Add eggs and 200 g milk then mix <nobr>30 sec\/speed 3.5<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add remaining 100 g milk and mix <nobr>30 sec\/speed 3.5<\/nobr>. Set aside in mixing bowl for 10 minutes. Place 1 knob of butter in a large pancake pan or frying pan and heat. When butter is hot, pour a ladle of dough into pan and spread over entire surface by turning the pan in a circular motion. The pancake must be quite thick. Cook for 2-3 minutes on each side, then transfer to a plate and set aside. Repeat until all batter has been used. Clean mixing bowl."]},{"title":"Chocolate Sauce","content":["Place chocolate in mixing bowl and grate <nobr>5 sec\/speed 10<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula then melt <nobr>5-6 min\/55°C\/speed 1<\/nobr> until melted.","Add cream and mix <nobr>30 sec\/speed 2.5<\/nobr>. Spread 1-2 Tbsp chocolate sauce over a pancake then place a whole banana on top and roll up pancake. Cut into slices (2 cm) and set aside on a serving plate. Repeat until all ingredients have been used. Serve or store in fridge until needed."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"Pancakes","content":["140 g plain flour","30 g cocoa powder","30 g caster sugar","1 pinch fine sea salt","2 medium eggs","300 g milk","unsalted butter, for frying"]},{"title":"Chocolate Sauce","content":["200 g milk chocolate, small pieces or callets","150 g double cream","5 bananas"]}],"id":"r308674","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-9PXD-wKeYGA\/XZWfrWXMhCI\/AAAAAAAAfIc\/mkel2u252hkq2CA2xpkzW8uvUKayHtX2wCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_zv4VZgwbratu4Ae8.png","title":"Banana Pancake Bites","publishedAt":"2018-03-24T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"1.7 g","fat":"4.3 g","uom":"per 1 piece","carbohydrates":"10.4 g","calories":"364 kJ \/ 86 kcal"},"usefulItems":"ladle, pancake pan or frying pan, hob, refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["Children can assist with this recipe, weighing ingredients in and setting the controls. Never leave them unattended with Thermomix®, while it is running or between steps.","Children can also help with assembly of the pancake bites."],"basicInfo":["easy","30m","45m","30 pieces"]}